Class VegetarianPizza

java.lang.Object
edu.mu.AbstractPizza.AbstractPizza
edu.mu.AbstractPizza.VegetarianPizza
public class VegetarianPizza extends AbstractPizza
Represents a vegetarian pizza, which includes toppings like tomato, cheese, bell pepper, black olive, and mushroom. Inherits from the AbstractPizza class.
